  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Description\r\n`ForkChoice.onAttestation` gets the state prior to calling `onForkChoiceThread` but all the attestation processing is done on the fork choice thread, when the validation and indexing could be done prior to jumping to the fork choice thread.  Only the actual vote updates need to be on the fork choice thread.\r\n\r\nWhen there are a large number of attestations, the fork choice thread may be highly contended so doing as much processing as possible before jumping to the single threaded portion avoids potential bottlenecks.",
